<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-02-0044 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book is a guide for conducting a socio-economic impact assessment,especially for large scale projets which may be controversial. It includesmitigation measures for resultant impacts, and goes beyond theory toexamine critical problems of implementation. In this volume the impactsof large-scale development projects in given geographic areas are considered.</TEXT></DOC>